talk about the resources of our
country or

10:22.522 --> 10:24.224 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
whether we're talking about
crime.

10:24.257 --> 10:30.296 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And to the point that was just
made about
speaking to individuals who are
competing

10:30.330 --> 10:36.803 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
with illegal labor for those
