Hincapie was
saying, is about fear-mongering?

11:12.472 --> 11:15.108 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KARTHICK RAMAKRISHNAN: Well,
there's a little
of both.

11:15.141 --> 11:16.843 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Right?

11:16.876 --> 11:20.313 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
