wage depression
effect.

11:41.601 --> 11:46.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
More generally, when we talk
about America
being strong, it's important to
remember that

11:46.506 --> 11:48.274 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
