11:48.308 --> 11:53.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, in fact, when you have seen
instances
like Riverside, New Jersey, for
example, which

11:53.746 --> 12:00.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
