12:12.899 --> 12:15.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: I'm going to let
Kris Kobach respond
to that, and then I will get to
you, Marielena

12:15.668 --> 12:17.403 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
