12:22.041 --> 12:24.577 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I would note George Borjas
of Harvard
University has talked about it.

12:24.611 --> 12:26.312 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And, look, it's just
commonsense.

12:26.346 --> 12:30.850 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anyone who is familiar with the
industries
of, like, meatpacking or hotel
janitorial

12:30.883 --> 12:36.189 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
