E-Verify requirements
in place.

12:51.437 --> 12:53.206 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Their economies are booming.

12:53.239 --> 12:57.610 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, clearly, pushing illegal
labor out of
the labor market doesn't mean
that a state's

12:57.644 --> 12:59.879 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
economy collapses, and the same
is true for
the country.

12:59.912 --> 13:04.150 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
