of crimes and
bad people, is the way he is
referring to

14:03.009 --> 14:05.445 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
us as immigrants -- that they
would be deported.

14:05.478 --> 14:10.083 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And what that really means in
practice, Gwen,
one is, it's an extreme
position, and it's

14:10.116 --> 14:11.884 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
an expensive position.

14:11.918 --> 14:15.621 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In order to deport and have a
deportation
force that would result in the
deportation

14:15.655 --> 14:22.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
of 11 million immigrants, we're
talking about
over $6 billion -- or $60
billion.

14:22.829 --> 14:27.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One of the things in terms of
the current
policies that many people don't
understand

14:27.200 --> 14:33.072 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
