thinks are
bad people that should be
deported?

14:47.153 --> 14:50.156 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
She's the grandmother of four
U.S. citizen
children.

14:50.189 --> 14:51.858 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
