that he, too, thought a wall was
justifiable.

15:58.758 --> 16:01.460 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, you know, that's really
interesting.

16:01.494 --> 16:03.896 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Obviously, Mr. Trump is not the
president
yet.

16:03.930 --> 16:05.097 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
